notes.text: Red Hat OpenShift Virtualization release 4.12.6 is now available with updates to packages and images that fix several bugs and add enhancements.
notes.title: Topic

notes.text:
OpenShift Virtualization is Red Hat's virtualization solution designed for Red Hat OpenShift Container Platform.

This advisory contains OpenShift Virtualization 4.12.6 images.
